Class NodeSetConstraintBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fuberlin.wiwiss.d2rq.nodes.NodeSetConstraintBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NodeSetFilter

    public class NodeSetConstraintBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements NodeSetFilter
    Builds up an Expression that expresses restrictions on a set of nodes. Used for expressing the constraints on a variable that is shared between node relations.
    Author:
    Richard Cyganiak (richard@cyganiak.de)
